jnxIfOtnMib.name: jnxIfOtnMib

revisions.description: Added OTN table entries for handling sub-port in the interface name. With suffix OCH2
This MIB module defines objects used for managing the OTN interface for Juniper products.
Added OTN Alarms and PM data.
